&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen at the WCH for an enthusiastic, motivated, and hardworking individual to join the team. You will be responsible for a quality service of food and beverages to our patients at ward level, following set procedures and specifications. This position requires flexibility to accommodate the needs of the service, good communication skills and a positive and professional attitude.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a part time post working 21 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Vilma Krisciuniene, Site Facilities Manager, 01736 874096&lt;/p&gt;
